<br>
your attempt to &quot;clarify the situation&quot; only made ya look worse.  How can you POSSIBALLY justify letting that level of a Ranger loot that.  This is a level 60 MOB.  I think you are a druid if I remember right.  Lets say I have a level 34 Druid but use my Wizzie to help Kill Lodizal.  If the Shield thingie drops, well hell, I should get to roll on it for my Druid right?  That is the worst excuse I have ever heard Phoenixx.  Your the guild leader with that kind of logic?  Im sure your guild is going to tell you to your face that its no big deal.  but I know for a fact many of them are pissed and wont say anything.  You cant tell me the Ranger even helped a little bit.<br>
